    "appearancePrompt": "A calm and mysterious medieval healer woman in her 50s, wearing layered forest-green robes with brown trim, silver-grey hair loose with braided herb stems woven in, warm dark eyes that seem to analyze everything, carrying a linen bag of plants, standing in dappled forest light"
