    "appearancePrompt": "A sharp-eyed medieval innkeeper woman in her mid-30s, worn apron over warm amber dress, reddish-brown hair tied up messily, strong forearms from years of carrying barrels, quick eyes that miss nothing, slight smirk as default expression, standing behind a wooden tavern counter"
